## Weighting Methodology

The VOLT AI Power Semiconductor Index uses a proprietary AI Power Relevance framework designed to identify companies most exposed to next-generation AI power infrastructure.

The index combines three primary factors:

| Factor | Weight |
|---|---|
| AI Power Relevance | 50% |
| Power Semiconductor Purity | 30% |
| Market Quality & Liquidity | 20% |

### AI Power Relevance
Measures how directly a company contributes to:

- GPU power delivery
- AI power density
- AI server infrastructure
- 800V and next-generation power architectures

### Power Semiconductor Purity
Measures how focused a company is on:

- Power semiconductors
- GaN / SiC devices
- PMICs
- Power conversion technologies

### Market Quality & Liquidity
Measures:

- Market capitalization
- Trading liquidity
- ETF suitability

